1. Download
    - wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.12.18/terraform_0.12.18_linux_amd64.zip

2. Unzip
    - unzip terraform_0.12.18_linux_amd64.zip


3. Configuration
    - edit /home/user_name/.profile
        add the following line at last 
        -----
        export PATH="$PATH:terraform_file_path/terraform"
        -----
4. Verifying
    - check 'terraform' command
    - check 'terraform -help' command
    - check 'terraform --help plan' command
